    "analysis": "We found pervasive anomalies in the 'socket' KPI across most candidate services (checkoutservice, currencyservice, emailservice, recommendationservice, and nearly all points for productcatalogservice) beginning ~2024-01-15 17:30:00 UTC. Disk I/O zeros appear for emailservice and recommendationservice, and emailservice also shows many low latency anomalies. According to the workflow, the next step is trace analysis to determine which faulty service is the most downstream faulty component in call chains and therefore the likely root cause. Traces will help distinguish which service(s) with socket anomalies are actually causing the failure vs. those merely affected.",
