    "instruction": "Load log.csv and parse timestamp with unit='s' and utc=True. Restrict to candidate services (checkoutservice, currencyservice, emailservice, productcatalogservice, recommendationservice) and to the incident window 2024-01-15 17:27:22 to 2024-01-15 17:57:22 UTC inclusive. For each cmdb_id compute: total_rows_in_window, sum_log_error_count (sum of log.error_count values), mean_log_row_count (mean of log.row_count values). Return a table with cmdb_id, total_rows_in_window, sum_log_error_count, mean_log_row_count sorted by sum_log_error_count desc. Also return up to 5 example log rows (timestamp, cmdb_id, log_name, value) for services where sum_log_error_count>0; if none have errors, return the top 5 rows by log.row_count. Limit the table to all candidate services (max 5 rows)." }

